<BaseLayout title="AI-Powered Podcast | David"><section class="hero shell"><p class="eyebrow">AI-powered podcast</p><h1>A security briefing designed for listening.</h1><p>CyberNews collects current cybersecurity reporting, prioritizes actively exploited and high-impact threats, and turns the result into a concise audio briefing.</p><div class="buttons"><a class="button primary" href={podcastUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Listen to the latest briefing</a></div></section><section class="section shell grid"><article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Collect</p><h3>Trusted reporting</h3><p>Security publications, government advisories, and vulnerability intelligence.</p></article><article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Prioritize</p><h3>Threat-first ordering</h3><p>Known exploitation and watched technologies rise above general news.</p></article><article class="card"><p class="eyebrow">Deliver</p><h3>Audio on your schedule</h3><p>A concise briefing for a commute, workout, or morning review.</p></article></section><section class="section shell"><div class="card"><h2>Responsible use of AI</h2><p>AI assists with summarization and narration. Important claims should still be verified against original reporting and authoritative advisories.</p></div></section></BaseLayout>
